attrib":{},"text":"2007—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/172/s11/a/4/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–172, § 11(a)(4)(A)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “with respect to gasoline used during the taxable year on a farm for farming purposes” before “(determined without regard to section 6420(g))”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/172/s11/a/4/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–172, § 11(a)(4)(B)","children":[],"tail":", which directed striking out “with respect to gasoline used during the taxable year: (A) otherwise than as a fuel in a highway vehicle; or (B) in vehicles while engaged in furnishing certain public passenger land transportation service”, was executed by striking out “with respect to gasoline used during the taxable year (A) otherwise than as a fuel in a highway vehicle or (B) in vehicles while engaged in furnishing certain public passenger land transportation service” before “(determined without regard to section 6421(i))”, to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/172/s11/a/4/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–172, § 11(a)(4)(C)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “with respect to fuels used for nontaxable purposes or resold during the taxable year” before “(determined without regard to section 6427(k))”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1998—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/206"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–206","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 6421(i)” for “section 6421(j)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/188"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–188","children":[],"tail":" amended par. (3) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (3) read as follows: “under section 6427—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(A) with respect to fuels used for nontaxable purposes or resold, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(B) with respect to any qualified diesel-powered highway vehicle purchased (or deemed purchased under section 6427(g)(6)),","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"during the taxable year (determined without regard to section 6427(k)).”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 6421(j) or 6427(k)” for “section 6421(i) or 6427(j)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1986—Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s1877/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, § 1877(a)","children":[],"tail":", amended par. (3) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (3) read as follows: “under section 6427 with respect to fuels used for nontaxable purposes or resold during the taxable year (determined without regard to section 6427(j)).”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/514/s1703/e/2/F"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–514, § 1703(e)(2)(F)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6427(k)” for “6427(j)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1984—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369/s471/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369, § 471(c)","children":[],"tail":", renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s39"},"text":"section 39 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369/s911/d/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369, § 911(d)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", which directed the amendment of par. (4) by substituting “6427(j)” for “6427(i)” was executed to par. (3) to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the redesignation of par. (4) as (3) by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/424"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–424","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/369/s911/d/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–369, § 911(d)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6427(j)” for “6427(i)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1983—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/424/s515/b/6/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–424, § 515(b)(6)(C)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “and special fuels” for “, special fuels, and lubricating oil” after “gasoline” in section catchline."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2) to (4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/424/s515/b/6/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–424, § 515(b)(6)(A)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “and” at end of par. (2), redesignated par. (4) as (3), and struck out former (3) which referred to amounts payable to the taxpayer under section 6424 with respect to lubricating oil used during the taxable year for certain nontaxable purposes (determined without regard to section 6424(f))."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/424/s515/b/6/B/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–424, § 515(b)(6)(B)(i)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6421 or 6427” for “6421, 6424, or 6427” after “amount payable under”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/424/s515/b/6/B/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–424, § 515(b)(6)(B)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6421(i) or 6427(i)” for “6421(i), 6424(f), or 6427(i)” after “and, under”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1980—Subsec. (a)(4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/223"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–223","children":[],"tail":" substituted “6427(i)” for “6427(h)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/223"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–223","children":[],"tail":" substituted “6427(i)” for “6427(h)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1978—Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/618"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–618","children":[],"tail":" substituted “for certain nontaxable purposes” for “otherwise than in a highway motor vehicle”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/599"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–599","children":[],"tail":" substituted “6427(h)” for “6427(g)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/599"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–599","children":[],"tail":" substituted “6427(h)” for “6427(g)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1906/b/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 1906(b)(8)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6420(g)” for “6420(h)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1906/b/9"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 1906(b)(9)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “6424(f)” for “6424(g)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/530"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–530","children":[],"tail":" substituted “6427(g)” for “6427(f)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/530"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–530","children":[],"tail":", which directed the amendment of subsec. (c) by substituting “6427(g)” for “6427(f)”, was executed to subsec. (b) to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the redesignation of subsec. (c) as (b) by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{}